  <brief_title>Pre-operative Counselling in Laryngectomized Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Pre-operative Speech-Language Pathology Counselling in Patients Undergoing to Total Laryngectomy: a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
